  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast is served in the restaurant and you can expect a good selection of cold goods on the buffet table as well as eggs and bacon.</p>
<p>After a busy day skiing, the hotel put on a delicious meal. Start off at the salad buffet before being served two courses to your table. It's then back up to the buffet table where a selection of sweet treats await. </p>
<p>On New Years Eve they serve a delicious gala dinner.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
