  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel La Villa is situated in the peaceful and snowy Boscdaplan area of La Villa in the stunning Alta Badia region. Surrounded by the spectacular Dolomites, the hotel is perfect for those wanting to immerse themselves in a tranquil setting after a busy day on the slopes. The hotel team will go to any length to ensure you have an enjoyable stay.</p>
<h2>Hotel shuttle</h2>
<p>The closest lift is the Gardenacchia, just 400 metres away and connecting you to the Badia area, great for intermediate skiing. If you are looking to head towards Corvara, San Cassiano and the Sella circuit, the hotel operates a daily shuttle to the Piz La Ila Gondola, home of the world cup Gran Risa run.</p>
<h2>Balcony &amp; Mountain View Rooms</h2>
<p>All bedrooms in the hotel not only have a balcony but also spectacular views of the surround mountains. Depending on the location of your bedroom, you can expect to wake up to either <span>Piz La Ila or Sass de la Crusc.</span></p>
<h2>Relaxation </h2>
<p>We all know there is nothing like a nice hot sauna after a day cruising on the slopes. The hotel's small wellness area is a welcoming way to chill once you get back from skiing. The steam room, relaxation area and sensory shower are all included in your holiday cost. There is a small local charge to use the single person whirlpool, definitely worth at least treating yourself once while on holiday. </p>]]></description>
